---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="global-footer">
  <div class="container footer-body">
    <div class="footer-brand">
      <img src="/logo.png" alt="GoolAPP" class="footer-logo" width="100" height="26" />
      <p class="footer-tagline">단순하고 직관적인 유틸리티 컬렉션</p>
    </div>
    <nav class="footer-nav" aria-label="하단 메뉴">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/privacy">개인정보처리방침</a></li>
        <li><a href="/terms">이용약관</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </div>
  <div class="container footer-bottom">
    <p>&copy; {currentYear} GoolAPP. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .global-footer {
    background: var(--color-surface-variant);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-outline-variant);
    padding: var(--space-12) 0 var(--space-6);
    margin-top: var(--space-20);
  }
  .footer-body {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-8);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }
  .footer-logo {
    height: 26px;
    width: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  .footer-tagline {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-on-surface-variant);
  }
  .footer-nav ul {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0; margin: 0;
  }
  .footer-nav a {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-on-surface-variant);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
  }
  .footer-nav a:hover { color: var(--color-primary); opacity: 1; }
  .footer-bottom {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-outline-variant);
    padding-top: var(--space-6);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .footer-bottom p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
    color: var(--color-on-surface-variant);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .footer-body { flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-6); }
    .footer-nav ul { flex-wrap: wrap; }
  }
</style>
